cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Promptise Foundry in academic work or production systems, please cite it."
title: "Promptise Foundry: A production framework for agentic AI systems"
abstract: >-
  Promptise Foundry is an open-source Python framework for building
  production-ready AI agent systems. It provides a composable reasoning
  engine, a native Model Context Protocol server and client, an
  autonomous agent runtime with crash recovery and governance, and a
  typed prompt engineering layer. All five modules share a common type
  system, observability pipeline, and security defaults.
